fragment_downloaded_cb({"url": "gtkcellarea-h.html#gtk_cell_area_request_renderer", "fragment": "Gtk.CellArea.RequestRenderer \nThis is a convenience function for Gtk.CellArea implementations to request size for cell renderers. It s important to use this function to request size and then use Gtk.CellArea.InnerCellArea at render and event time since this function will add padding around the cell for focus painting. \nParameters \nthe Gtk.CellRenderer to request size for \nthe Gtk.Orientation in which to request size \nthe Gtk.Widget that area is rendering onto \nthe allocation contextual size to request for or if the base request for the orientation is to be returned. \nlocation to store the minimum size or null \nlocation to store the natural size or null \nSince \n"});